        "name": "厂长·老李",
        "avatar": "textures/npcs/foreman_li.png",
        "side": "left"
      },
      "text": "我们工厂有三条生产线：橡胶原材、塑料成型和合成加工。每条线都有自己的秘密...",
      "emotion": "thoughtful",
      "audio": "sounds/dialogue/factory_info.ogg",
      "choices": [
        {
          "choice_id": "c4",
          "text": "橡胶线有什么特别？",
          "next_node": "rubber_line",
          "effects": {
            "knowledge_rubber": 1
          }
        },
        {
          "choice_id": "c5",
          "text": "我想回去重新选择",
          "next_node": "start",
          "effects": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "node_id": "work_assignment",
      "speaker": {
        "name": "厂长·老李",
        "avatar": "textures/npcs/foreman_li.png",
        "side": "left"
      },
      "text": "很好，直接去B区报到吧。记住，不要问太多问题。",
